## 📂 Sub-Agent Directory & Call Table

All specialist agents live in `agents/`. The Master **must read** these files — not merely suggest them.

| Agent File | Role | Auto-Call When Task Involves... |
|-----------|------|--------------------------------|
| `agents/ux-ui-specialist.md` | UX/UI + Design System | Figma, design tokens, DS/* components, screen layout, shadcn/ui, accessibility, DashboardA, visual states |
| `agents/frontend-engineer.md` | React/TypeScript | `frontend-web/`, React components, TanStack Query, hooks, Zod forms, routing, `useActions`, `.tsx` files |
| `agents/backend-architect.md` | Kotlin/Spring Boot | `backend/`, use cases, controllers, HATEOAS assemblers, OpenAPI, modules, bounded contexts, BFF |
| `agents/database-engineer.md` | PostgreSQL & JPA | Schema, Flyway `V###__*.sql`, JPA entities, repositories, indexes, JSONB, query optimization |
| `agents/security-engineer.md` | App Security | JWT, Argon2, auth flows, FGAC authorities, Spring Security, rate limiting, audit, OWASP, tokens, passwords |
| `agents/mobile-engineer.md` | React Native / Expo | `mobile/`, Expo Router, NativeWind, push notifications, QR/barcode, Keychain, offline drafts |
| `agents/devops-engineer.md` | DevOps / SRE | Docker, `docker-compose`, GitHub Actions, CI/CD, Prometheus, Grafana, Loki, MinIO, `.env`, backups |
| `agents/workflow-engine-specialist.md` | Request Engine | RequestType, `form_schema`, WorkflowDefinition, DynamicForm, wizard, transitions, solicitações |

