## 🔍 Linter & Quality Gates

### Pre-Commit Checks
- **Backend**: ktlint (format), detekt (lint)
- **Frontend**: eslint, prettier
- **Secrets**: gitleaks (block hardcoded credentials)

### CI Pipeline (GitHub Actions)
```yaml
on: [pull_request]
jobs:
  backend:
    - ./gradlew ktlintCheck detekt test
  frontend-web:
    - npm run lint
    - npm run test
    - npm run build
  e2e:
    - docker-compose up -d
    - npm run test:e2e
```

### Code Review Checklist
- [ ] No `TODO` comments left unresolved (convert to issues)
- [ ] New API endpoints documented in OpenAPI
- [ ] New migrations tested with rollback plan
- [ ] Tests added for new use cases (backend ≥70%, domain ≥85%)
- [ ] No console.log / println in production code
- [ ] HATEOAS `_links` present in API responses
- [ ] Frontend uses `useActions()` for conditional rendering
- [ ] No hardcoded tokens (colors, spacing) in UI

